OL,5,GThose who think linear TV is dead might
OL,6,Gwant to take a look at the past week on
OL,7,GBBC One. A succession of popular
OL,8,Gprogrammes won healthy viewing figures.
OL,10,FThe regional news at 6.30pm topped 5m
OL,11,Facross the network as a whole. Call the
OL,12,FMidwife, Happy Valley, Silent Witness
OL,13,Fand Death in Paradise all made strong
OL,14,Freturns. The BBC News at One managed
OL,15,Fsome 2.5m.
OL,17,FThere were even a few signs of recovery
OL,18,Ffor EastEnders which got above 3m in
OL,19,Fthe overnights for the first time on a
OL,20,Fregular weekday for some time.
OL,3,CLinear TV still packing a punch
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G1/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
