OL,5,FPerhaps most remarkably, The Apprentice
OL,6,Freturned with an audience bigger than
OL,7,Flast time round ` after inheriting a
OL,8,Fgood rating from Dragons' Den. Both
OL,9,Fthese programmes started out on BBC Two
OL,10,Fand didn't originally seem like obvious
OL,11,Fcandidates for moves to the main
OL,12,Fchannel.
OL,14,FSo what do they all have in common? All
OL,15,Fthose programmes debuted on BBC One `
OL,16,Fthey didn't drop on the iPlayer
OL,17,Fearlier.
OL,3,CLinear TV still packing a punch
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G2/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35903
