PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1675159471
OL,5,FFans of Happy Valley will have to wait
OL,6,Funtil 9pm on Sunday for the next
OL,7,Fepisode. Not that you'd know it from
OL,8,Fsome of the promotional push for
OL,9,FiPlayer ` some of the time the main
OL,10,Fchannel is not even being mentioned.
OL,12,FWell, of course, only luddites pretend
OL,13,Fthe iPlayer is not becoming
OL,14,Fincreasingly important. Who wouldn't
OL,15,Fwant to catch up on programmes they've
OL,16,Fmissed or start the show at the
OL,17,Fbeginning if they've tuned in late.
OL,19,FBut how about this for a mixed economy?
OL,20,FShows dropping on the iPlayer as they
OL,21,F"drop" on BBC One.
OL,3,CLinear TV still packing a punch
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G3/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
