OL,5,FIf the revival of Waterloo Road is a
OL,6,Fsuccess, that's exactly how you could
OL,7,Fmarket the scheduling to its young
OL,8,Ffans. New episodes at 8pm on Tuesdays
OL,9,Feither on iPlayer or BBC One.
OL,11,FAll this is a reminder of why major
OL,12,Flinear channels are so important ` they
OL,13,Ffocus on live and quality, original
OL,14,Fcontent and have the potential to make
OL,15,Fa real impact.
OL,3,CLinear TV still packing a punch
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G4/8
