PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1675159471
OL,5,FEven the immediate ratings for Harry
OL,6,Fand Meghan's interviews on Netflix in
OL,7,Fthe UK were modest compared to those of
OL,8,Fmany BBC One and ITV 1 shows even if
OL,9,Fthe repercussions of these programmes
OL,10,Fwere huge.
OL,12,FRemind me of the cost of Netflix or
OL,13,FAmazon Prime against the cost of a TV
OL,14,Flicence?
OL,16,FThere is an important distinction to be
OL,17,Fdrawn between whether major linear
OL,18,Fchannels have a future and whether,
OL,19,Fsay, Freeview or satellite remain as
OL,20,Fmethods of distribution.
OL,3,CLinear TV still packing a punch
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G5/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
