OL,5,FPresentation has a role in this too.
OL,6,FLive continuity done well adds to the
OL,7,Fsense of occasion and reminds viewers
OL,8,Fthey are not alone. They remind the
OL,9,Fviewer the channel they are watching is
OL,10,Fthe living product of a lot of
OL,11,Ftalented, creative people ` not a
OL,12,Fserver loaded up with 6 episodes of a
OL,13,F1990s comedy.
OL,15,FIt will be interesting to see if a
OL,16,F"thinning out" of minor linear channels
OL,17,Factually reinforces the positions of
OL,18,Fthe major players.
OL,3,CLinear TV still packing a punch
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G6/8
